Question 4: Todo Management API
Task:
Build Todo CRUD APIs using MongoDB.
Todo Schema:
{
title: String,
completed: Boolean,
priority: String
}

APIs:
● POST /todos
● GET /todos
● GET /todos/:id

● PUT /todos/:id
● DELETE /todos/:id
Constraints:
● title required
● Default completed value should be false
● priority can be:
○ low
○ medium
○ high
Bonus:
Create API:
GET /todos/completed

Return all completed todos.